---
title: Roasted Sweet Potato and Ginger Garlic Chicken Stew with Lime and Spinach
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Roasted Sweet Potato & Chicken Stew in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
